<ul>
<li>Black, Cheryl A.; H. Andrew Black; and Stephen A. Marlett (eds.) The Zapotec Grammar Files. <a href="http://www.sil.org/mexico/WorkPapers/WP001i-ZapotecGrammarFiles.htm" class="external free" rel="nofollow">http://www.sil.org/mexico/WorkPapers/WP001i-ZapotecGrammarFiles.htm</a></li>
